rows.label: tlk45500153_06_msg0001
rows.name:
Here's a bit of gossip I heard
at the baths.

rows.label: tlk45500153_06_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently the Luxurian Divine Beast has
shown its face in the Cloud Sea for the
first time in forever!

rows.label: tlk45500153_06_msg0003
rows.name:
Nobody had a clue where it was lurking
for years and years... I wonder what
prompted this sudden development.

rows.label: tlk45500153_06_msg0004
rows.name:
Rumor has it that something very
sinister might be afoot.

rows.label: tlk45500153_06_msg0005
rows.name:
Though we seem to have a decent
relationship with them, so I suppose
it could be a good thing for trade!
